metadata.name: Lost Soul #1 "The Monk"
metadata.description:
While meditating for a little too long, this soul forgot to return to its host, and now walks endlessly on the shores of the River Styx.

Head: Carved Jade
Eye: Powerful Glow (White)
Body: Carved Jade
Core: Powerful Glow (White), Jade Ohm Necklace
Cuffs: Jade Bracelet
